    // polite live region so its appearance is announced to assistive tech — a
    // plain <div> is silent and the previous results vanish with no
    // explanation. role="status" maps to an implicit aria-live="polite" region,
    // and because the wrapper has no text of its own its accessible name must
    // come from aria-label.
